Middleman Bot Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to Middleman! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.

2. Information We Collect
Middleman collects the following types of information:

2.1 User Data
User IDs: To identify and manage user interactions.
Join Dates: To record when users join the server.
Role Assignments: To manage and assign roles appropriately.
Feedback and Interaction Records: To enhance user experience and service quality.
2.2 Server Data
Server IDs: To identify and manage server-specific settings.
Channel IDs: To facilitate communication within specific channels.
Message IDs: For moderation and interaction tracking.
3. How We Use Your Information
The information collected is used for the following purposes:

Service Provision: To deliver and improve the features and functionalities of Middleman.
User Management: To manage user roles, permissions, and interactions.
Communication: To send welcome messages, notifications, and updates.
Feedback Analysis: To collect and analyze user feedback for service enhancement.
4. Data Storage and Security
4.1 Data Storage
All data is stored within Discordâ€™s infrastructure and is not transferred or stored off-platform.

4.2 Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. These measures include encryption and access controls.

5. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not share, sell, or disclose your personal information to third parties, except as required by law or to protect our rights and services.

6. Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access: Request access to the personal information we hold about you.
Correction: Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information.
Deletion: Request deletion of your personal information, subject to certain exceptions.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on our website or through the bot. Continued use of Middleman after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

8. Contact Us
